    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"stop fighting the current\"... that sounds peaceful, i guess. but it feels more like just giving up. like i'm just accepting that there's nothing left to save. do you really think it's okay to just... stop trying to be okay? to just accept that i'm never going to be whole again?",
